# Deterministic line endings on every platform. This is LOAD-BEARING beyond
# style: the transpiler replay cache is keyed on prompts that embed each
# COBOL source file's SHA-256, so source bytes must be identical on every
# checkout or the committed cache stops replaying offline. Everything text
# normalizes to LF; binaries are marked so no filter ever touches them.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary artifacts (auto-detection would get these right, but be explicit).
*.jar binary
*.png binary
*.ico binary
